    • Method Detail

      • run

        public void run()
        Performs the partial query and stores the result in result. A XML-document is generated from the key-value-pairs in the sub-query for both nodes and ways and the specific bounding-box. This document is sent to the Overpass-API via HTTP-POST and the resulting XML-document is sent back. If no error is reported, the result is a XML-document listing all nodes and ways suitable for the request. POIs are generated from the nodes and by picking a node from the ways returned. After the result is stored this thread terminates.

        For information about the Overpass-API in general confer this document and for information about the language to be used read this guide.

        run in interface java.lang.Runnable
